metadata.name: Beyond The Face - #01
metadata.description: "Beyond the Face" is an intriguing collection of abstract art that delves into the depths of the human psyche, pushing the boundaries of traditional portraiture. Through the use of bold lines, vibrant colors, and imaginative forms, each piece takes on a life of its own, inviting the viewer to explore the complexities of the human experience. From the fragmented geometry of Cubism to the dreamlike landscapes of Surrealism, these works challenge our perceptions of reality and offer a new perspective on the essence of the self.
